00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 13=

4
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,550
Do you even know
what a male escort house is?

5
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,560
Of course I do.

6
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,040
A place for male companions.

7
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:43,000
Then why are you enjoying it so much?

8
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,580
Since we're already here,

9
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:45,959
we should blend in.

10
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:48,040
Otherwise it'll be too easy
to expose ourselves.

11
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,760
You just enjoy watching them.

12
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:51,359
You really do know me well.

13
00:01:54,519 --> 00:01:55,359
Still looking?

14
00:01:58,520 --> 00:02:00,040
You're better looking than all of them.

15
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,159
Shen Zhinian.

16
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,719
I'm helping you carry out your task.

17
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,680
This place only receives female guests.

18
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,719
If a man wants to enter,

19
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,600
he can only come
as a female guest's attendant.

20
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:10,080
If I act too serious,

21
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,599
won't people grow suspicious?

22
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:12,919
How do you know that?

23
00:02:13,180 --> 00:02:14,120
You've been here before?

24
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,360
Guess.

25
00:02:15,790 --> 00:02:16,960
The auction's about to begin.

26
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:19,960
Mm.

27
00:02:22,479 --> 00:02:23,479
We'll split up.

28
00:02:23,660 --> 00:02:24,639
Stay here and keep watch.

29
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,400
Don't let anyone buy the item.

30
00:02:26,639 --> 00:02:27,159
Yes.

31
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,360
Wen Ling,

32
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,680
go scout the surroundings.

33
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,400
Yes.

34
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:41,680
Young Master,
Jiang Fu and Lu Jianglin are here.

35
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:49,159
They're Father's men.

36
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,840
Luckily Jiang Fu has never met me before.

37
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,639
What exactly is being auctioned tonight?

38
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,319
Should we notify His Majesty?

39
00:02:58,850 --> 00:02:59,919
Let's wait a little longer.

40
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:01,660
We'll see once the auction begins.

41
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,120
Mm.

42
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,599
So it's fruit wine.

43
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:11,199
Rich aroma. A fine wine.

44
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,759
Your injuries haven't healed yet.

45
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:13,719
You shouldn't drink.

46
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,000
Your Majesty,

47
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:18,520
this is my first time attending
a lantern festival.

48
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,080
My first time entering
a male escort house.

49
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:21,800
My first time drinking
in a pleasure house.

50
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:26,159
I used to think
people should always live by the rules.

51
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,879
But now I feel

52
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:29,520
that while we're alive,

53
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:30,560
we should see more

54
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:32,039
and experience more.

55
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,319
Cold hearted.

56
00:03:39,879 --> 00:03:40,919
Sharp tongued.

57
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,639
Shen Zhinian,

58
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:46,190
I think sneaking out of the palace
has truly made you fearless.

59
00:03:49,580 --> 00:03:50,439
Seal it with a stamp.

60
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:53,290
In my next life, I'll become a leopard
and come find Your Majesty again.

61
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,199
Seal it with a stamp.

62
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,120
In the next life,

63
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:03,000
Mother can be my daughter.

64
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,550
How many people are you trying to stamp?

65
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,520
Ah?

66
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,479
Nothing.

67
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:13,439
The auction begins now.

68
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,120
The first item,

69
00:04:15,130 --> 00:04:17,550
a gold bracelet once owned by
an imperial consort of the former dynasty.

70
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,199
Starting bid, one hundred taels.

71
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:21,920
- Is this the item?
- Two hundred taels.

72
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,279
Three hundred taels.

73
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,199
Any higher bids?

74
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:26,439
No.

75
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,040
Three hundred taels, first call.

76
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,360
Do you really recognize the item?

77
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,279
Three hundred taels, second call.

78
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:33,000
Sure...

79
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,800
- Sure...
- Fine. Four hundred taels.

80
00:04:36,279 --> 00:04:38,399
You'd better handle this properly.

81
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,879
If we return empty handed tonight...

82
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,720
Six hundred taels.

83
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,279
Then prepare to lose your head.

84
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:44,120
Seven hundred taels.

85
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,560
Yes.

86
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:47,120
Sold.

87
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:48,839
Second item,

88
00:04:49,439 --> 00:04:50,360
Wen Qianji.

89
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,710
This item was handcrafted by
an imperial consort of the former dynasty.

90
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:56,040
Playing with it daily
can make the fingers slender

91
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,199
and the skin smooth as jade.

92
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,439
This is the item.

93
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,879
Starting bid,

94
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:00,600
one hundred taels.

95
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:03,780
(One hundred taels)

96
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,800
Room Xing bids one hundred taels.

97
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:10,639
Room Yue,

98
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:11,439
three hundred taels.

99
00:05:13,399 --> 00:05:14,879
Room Xing, four hundred taels.

100
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:17,439
Room Yue, eight hundred taels.

101
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,720
If this bidding keeps going,

102
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,290
it'll be disadvantageous to Your Majesty.

103
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,040
Do you have a plan?

104
00:05:30,399 --> 00:05:31,040
Who is it?

105
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,120
Oh dear.

106
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,399
Sorry, wrong room.

107
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:39,040
The young escort beside you, Madam,

108
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,120
is exceptionally handsome.

109
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:42,079
Why have I never seen him before?

110
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,279
I brought him with me.

111
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:51,480
Madam, would you be willing
to let me have him?

112
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,480
Get lost.

113
00:05:54,090 --> 00:05:55,240
Please don't be angry, Madam.

114
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,000
I'll leave at once.

115
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:57,000
Leaving now.

116
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:02,600
Still outside?

117
00:06:03,079 --> 00:06:03,959
Room Xing,

118
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:04,800
one thousand taels.

119
00:06:04,810 --> 00:06:06,090
What are you standing there for?

120
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:07,439
Pour me some wine already.

121
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,720
One thousand five hundred taels.

122
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:12,959
Room Xing, two thousand taels.

123
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,360
Drink up.

124
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:18,279
And this is how you're serving me wine?

125
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:20,079
I'm not drinking.

126
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:22,120
Don't use this as an excuse
to stir up trouble.

127
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,800
Doesn't Your Majesty want

128
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,160
to stall for time

129
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,120
so Jiang Chen can keep bidding?

130
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:55,940
I deeply regret
disturbing you earlier, Madam.

131
00:06:55,959 --> 00:06:57,639
I've come especially

132
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,720
to offer you a toast.

133
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,759
The young escort beside you, Madam,

134
00:07:06,759 --> 00:07:08,160
is truly stunning.

135
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:10,000
I wonder whether Madam would be willing

136
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,279
to let me join in?

137
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,279
Absolutely not.

138
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:14,920
He's my favorite little companion.

139
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,079
I don't share.

140
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,639
What a pity.

141
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,120
And who might you be?

142
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:30,519
He's my little companion too.

143
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:43,439
Madam, you certainly have exquisite taste.

144
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,879
Why aren't you coming over?

145
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,000
Learn from your older brother.

146
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,240
Then I won't disturb you any longer.

147
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,759
Madam, please enjoy yourselves.

148
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,120
What do we do now?

149
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:21,319
Drink.

150
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:26,160
Madam.

151
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:29,360
What are you doing?

152
00:08:29,839 --> 00:08:31,319
Wasn't I supposed to serve Madam wine?

153
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,519
Drink it yourself.

154
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:40,799
Then should I remove my clothes as well?

155
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,240
That's unnecessary.

156
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,720
I was only asking.

157
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,600
Didn't I tell you
to stay downstairs and bid?

158
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,879
Why did you come up?

159
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,720
I left Luo Hao downstairs to wait.

160
00:08:58,160 --> 00:09:00,399
But the price has already
risen to ten thousand taels.

161
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:02,320
I didn't bring enough silver.

162
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,559
According to Jinsong Pavilion's rules,

163
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:06,620
you must have enough silver
on hand to place a bid.

164
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,990
So I came up to ask Your Majesty
whether you've brought enough silver.

165
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,799
Let them bid.

166
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:16,159
Room Xing bids thirteen thousand taels.

167
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,559
Any higher bids?

168
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:20,840
Thirteen thousand taels, first call.

169
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:22,799
Thirteen thousand taels, second call.

170
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,879
Thirteen thousand taels, third call.

171
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:26,759
Sold.

172
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,879
Good.

173
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:32,360
Thirteen thousand taels

174
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,600
for this worthless thing.

175
00:09:36,039 --> 00:09:37,080
Lu Jianglin,

176
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:40,159
if this doesn't contain
what Duke Zhen wants,

177
00:09:40,799 --> 00:09:43,919
I'll have you torn apart
and fed to the dogs.

178
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:44,879
Yes.

179
00:09:47,559 --> 00:09:49,080
How do you open this thing?

180
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,519
I don't know either.

181
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,720
Move aside.

182
00:10:26,679 --> 00:10:28,120
- Farewell, Your Majesty.
- Farewell, Your Majesty.

183
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:37,000
No idea what it even is.

184
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,090
His Majesty wants it,

185
00:10:38,279 --> 00:10:39,320
and so does Duke Zhen.

186
00:10:39,330 --> 00:10:41,180
Willing to spend
over ten thousand taels on it.

187
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,559
The military tally.

188
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,399
What?

189
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:45,960
Although His Majesty
controls the troops in the capital,

190
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,560
they're nowhere near strong enough
to rival the Zhen State Army.

191
00:10:48,879 --> 00:10:51,519
That's how he maintained peace
with Father before.

192
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,190
But Father's ambitions
are growing greater and greater.

193
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,480
If His Majesty wishes
to contend with him,

194
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,440
he must find the Chifeng Army

195
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,990
left behind by his maternal grandfather.

196
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,600
But didn't the Chifeng Army

197
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,759
get wiped out ten years ago?

198
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,130
The commander died in battle,

199
00:11:04,570 --> 00:11:07,000
and the remaining forces scattered
across different regions.

200
00:11:07,370 --> 00:11:09,120
As long as
the military tally is recovered,

201
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:10,360
they can all be gathered again.

202
00:11:10,759 --> 00:11:12,590
If the box truly contains
the military tally,

203
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,919
then war may break out very soon.

204
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:17,000
For Young Master,

205
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:18,480
would that be good or bad?

206
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:19,679
What do you think?

207
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:22,690
Everyone says Young Master
is indifferent to fame and ambition,

208
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,600
gentle and righteous,

209
00:11:23,919 --> 00:11:25,240
and even turned against Duke Zhen

210
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,320
to protect His Majesty.

211
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:30,159
But I feel that you
have plans of your own.

212
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,879
Everyone has plans of their own.

213
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,840
Send a secret message to Father.

214
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:35,990
The military tally has fallen
into His Majesty's hands.

215
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,780
What do you mean by this, Young Master?

216
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:51,950
(I never expected that
after searching for so many years,)

217
00:11:52,279 --> 00:11:54,159
(I would truly find it.)

218
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,240
Is Your Majesty unable to open the box?

219
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,159
Want to give it a try?

220
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:03,720
Yes.

221
00:12:04,070 --> 00:12:05,480
If you open it, you'll be rewarded.

222
00:12:05,919 --> 00:12:07,240
If you fail,

223
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,840
then you'll be punished.

224
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:15,080
This looks like a puzzle box.

225
00:12:15,090 --> 00:12:16,860
As long as the characters
are arranged correctly,

226
00:12:16,879 --> 00:12:18,360
it should open.

227
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:22,440
(These characters together...)

228
00:12:22,759 --> 00:12:25,639
(sound like a song
from my previous life.)

229
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:28,000
Phoenix.

230
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:30,000
Perches.

231
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,279
Parasol.

232
00:12:33,399 --> 00:12:34,679
Long.

233
00:12:35,399 --> 00:12:36,559
Night.

234
00:12:37,799 --> 00:12:38,919
Bright.

235
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:42,639
(She actually knows the secret code?)

236
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:44,679
It opened.

237
00:12:49,039 --> 00:12:51,120
Is this what Your Majesty
has been searching for?

238
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,440
Then today, I've completed

239
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:58,039
the task Your Majesty assigned me.

240
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,200
Your Majesty,

241
00:12:59,679 --> 00:13:01,399
may I have my death-exemption medal now?

242
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:17,680
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

243
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:24,640
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

244
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:28,640
♪If we don't meet♪

245
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:32,080
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

246
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:38,800
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

247
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:45,600
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

248
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:52,280
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

249
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:59,480
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

250
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:06,360
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

251
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:12,480
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

252
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:20,000
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

253
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:26,840
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

254
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:33,560
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

